abilities.name: Split Shot
abilities.description: Medusa magically splits her shot into several arrows. These arrows deal a lower percent of her normal damage. The extra targets will not receive other attack effects (such as critical strike).

abilities.name: Mystic Snake
abilities.description: A mystic snake made of energy jumps from target to target dealing damage and stealing mana. After it reaches its last target, it returns to Medusa to replenish her with mana. The snake deals more damage per jump and steals 11/14/17/20% of the targets' total mana. Deals Pure damage to units petrified by Stone Gaze. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.
abilities.upgrade_description: Causes Mystic Snake to turn enemies into stone for %stone_form_scepter_base% second, increases by  %stone_form_scepter_increment% seconds per bounce.

abilities.name: Mana Shield
abilities.description: Creates a shield that absorbs 60% of the incoming damage in exchange for Medusa's mana.

abilities.name: Stone Gaze
abilities.description: Any enemy units looking at Medusa will have their movement and attack speed slowed.  If 2 seconds of total time is accumulated looking at Medusa while Stone Gaze is active, that unit will turn to stone.  Petrified units are stunned, and take bonus physical damage.

talents.name: +2.5s Stone Gaze Duration
talents.description: The duration of the stun is not affected.

talents.name: Split Shot Uses Modifiers
talents.description: Allows on-hit effects to apply to the secondary attacks from Split Shot.
